- No, he knew it.

753
01:01:18,297 --> 01:01:21,028
Tell me the truth, did you tell him?

754
01:01:28,400 --> 01:01:30,914
Get your stuff, let's go to Mom's

755
01:01:31,210 --> 01:01:33,389
What about Grandpa?
- We'll take him.

756
01:01:33,680 --> 01:01:35,910
I have homework... I'm not going.

757
01:01:36,526 --> 01:01:39,149
I'll leave you alone and you'll be
scared...  - OK.

758
01:01:40,138 --> 01:01:43,332
If you call for me to come back then
I will have a problem

759
01:01:53,640 --> 01:01:56,518
He didn't even say "don't go, don't
do it...

760
01:01:56,771 --> 01:01:59,270
... I won't divorce you"...

761
01:01:59,390 --> 01:02:03,070
... as though it was nothing that I
lived with him for 14 years

762
01:02:42,908 --> 01:02:44,633
Father!

763
01:02:46,600 --> 01:02:48,397
What are you doing here?

764
01:02:49,538 --> 01:02:51,239
Why did you come?

765
01:02:52,106 --> 01:02:55,915
Didn't you have an exam today?
- No, tomorrow.

766
01:02:56,951 --> 01:02:58,911
Who are you here with?

767
01:03:02,680 --> 01:03:03,527
Hello.

768
01:03:04,741 --> 01:03:09,118
Why didn't you call and tell us you had
gotten into trouble?

769
01:03:09,238 --> 01:03:10,918
I didn't want to impose

770
01:03:11,038 --> 01:03:13,080
Silly man.

771
01:03:13,200 --> 01:03:16,329
Sit down.
- No, we have to take him to a hearing

772
01:03:18,215 --> 01:03:21,511
Where is your grandfather?
- In safe hands... don't worry

773
01:03:21,631 --> 01:03:24,669
... they keep saying "my baby,
my baby"...

774
01:03:24,950 --> 01:03:29,628
.. as if their 18-year-old son
was stabbed to death.

775
01:03:29,748 --> 01:03:31,480
Did you talk to her?

776
01:03:31,600 --> 01:03:36,948
You can't ever to talk the husband, to
her I said, sweetheart, you are young...

777
01:03:37,068 --> 01:03:40,195
... next year you can have another child

778
01:03:42,228 --> 01:03:43,399
What happened?

779
01:03:43,520 --> 01:03:46,159
I have to get the home valued
- Okay, go.

780
01:03:46,279 --> 01:03:47,679
Hello.
- Hello.

781
01:03:47,799 --> 01:03:49,875
You stay here, I'll be back
- Okay, go

782
01:03:55,191 --> 01:03:56,759
Thank you.

783
01:03:58,864 --> 01:04:01,624
Hello, Mrs. Lavasani.
- Hi, how are you?

784
01:04:01,744 --> 01:04:03,660
I'm fine, you?
- Sorry to trouble you

785
01:04:03,780 --> 01:04:06,797
No, it's no trouble, I'm glad I ran
into you...

786
01:04:07,040 --> 01:04:09,504
... is what they are saying true?

787
01:04:09,624 --> 01:04:12,557
Unfortunately, he pushed her, she fell
and she lost her child

788
01:04:13,032 --> 01:04:14,718
So, what am I supposed to say?

789
01:04:14,838 --> 01:04:17,190
I don't know what they will ask you

790
01:04:17,310 --> 01:04:20,393
What if they ask me something against
your husband?

791
01:04:21,640 --> 01:04:23,870
I think you should tell the truth

792
01:04:24,128 --> 01:04:26,999
Please do not stop there.
- Where was he?

793
01:04:27,119 --> 01:04:29,237
Mr. Lavasani was in the kitchen

794
01:04:29,357 --> 01:04:34,017
Did he say anything or react at all?
- If he did, I didn't notice

795
01:04:34,137 --> 01:04:38,558
- How did you know she was pregnant?
- I think she told me

796
01:04:39,255 --> 01:04:41,954
You asked, ma'am, why would I
have said anything?

797
01:04:42,891 --> 01:04:46,275
Her daughter was drawing a picture
of a man and a woman

798
01:04:46,779 --> 01:04:48,556
"This is my mother and father", she
said.

799
01:04:48,676 --> 01:04:51,552
I said, "honey, your mom isn't that fat"
and she said she had a child in her belly

800
01:04:51,672 --> 01:04:54,396
You didn't know she was pregnant from
her appearance?  - No.

801
01:04:54,684 --> 01:04:57,508
Why do you lie? You are a woman...

802
01:04:57,628 --> 01:05:00,720
.. you can't tell from someone's looks
that they are pregnant?

803
01:05:00,840 --> 01:05:05,311
Okay, even if I could tell, it does
make a difference for Mr. Lavasani

804
01:05:06,800 --> 01:05:10,787
This woman is his daughter's teacher.
They have colluded to tell the same story

805
01:05:10,907 --> 01:05:13,992
- Why are you being rude to her?
- No one is speaking to you

806
01:05:14,239 --> 01:05:16,598
When could we match our stories?

807
01:05:16,718 --> 01:05:18,248
I was here last night.

808
01:05:18,368 --> 01:05:20,836
One thing is clear. Right now as we
speak...

809
01:05:21,000 --> 01:05:24,800
... that man could hear what we were
discussing, am I right?

810
01:05:24,920 --> 01:05:30,711
Ma'am, I didn't hear you... my mind was
preoccupied with my own problems

811
01:05:31,656 --> 01:05:34,432
Why would I listen to your conversation?

812
01:05:34,824 --> 01:05:37,860
... should I swear by Allah?
- As if you believe in God!

813
01:05:37,980 --> 01:05:40,240
No, God is just for guys like you.

814
01:05:40,360 --> 01:05:42,396
Let's take a break for a moment

815
01:05:43,971 --> 01:05:45,843
He is a decent man...

816
01:05:45,963 --> 01:05:48,879
... I've been tutoring his daughter
for one year...

817
01:05:49,120 --> 01:05:50,960
... he's truly not like that.

818
01:05:51,080 --> 01:05:55,109
Why wouldn't she tell me she was
pregnant? Why did she hide it?

819
01:05:55,229 --> 01:05:57,331
If I knew she was pregnant, I wouldn't
hire her

820
01:05:57,451 --> 01:06:01,106
Why did you hire when you knew she
didn't have her husband's permission?

821
01:06:01,226 --> 01:06:03,716
Thank you. You can go, thank you.

822
01:06:03,880 --> 01:06:04,949
Thank you.

823
01:06:08,523 --> 01:06:13,138
"During the age of Sasarian the people
were divided into two classes ...

824
01:06:13,258 --> 01:06:20,310
...the privileged upper class and the
class of the normal people"

825
01:06:20,840 --> 01:06:22,398
"Normal class."

826
01:06:26,861 --> 01:06:28,616
- What did they ask?

827
01:06:28,736 --> 01:06:32,072
If your father knew that she was
pregnant.

828
01:06:32,554 --> 01:06:35,242
I'm sorry the trouble you had to go
through

829
01:06:35,362 --> 01:06:37,580
It's okay, it's no trouble

830
01:06:39,400 --> 01:06:41,637
Honey, what happened to cause your
mom to lose her baby?

831
01:06:41,757 --> 01:06:43,497
Her stomach hurt

832
01:06:44,925 --> 01:06:46,449
Why did her stomach hurt?

833
01:06:47,395 --> 01:06:49,670
Did your dad fight with her at home?

834
01:06:50,299 --> 01:06:52,628
Why would they have fought?

835
01:06:52,903 --> 01:06:56,715
Maybe he was mad that she was working
in someone's home without telling him

836
01:06:56,835 --> 01:07:00,112
Did he hit your mom?
- My parents don't fight at all.

837
01:07:00,440 --> 01:07:05,049
So, why were your mom and dad fighting
in that picture you drew?

838
01:07:05,169 --> 01:07:08,313
You showed me.
- They don't fight anymore.

839
01:07:08,666 --> 01:07:12,350
They don't fight any more? Are you sure?

840
01:07:16,689 --> 01:07:19,195
Yesterday he said he didn't know
that she was pregnant

841
01:07:19,617 --> 01:07:21,731
... now he is saying he didn't even push
her

842
01:07:21,851 --> 01:07:24,434
... and you just stand there staring at
me without saying anything

843
01:07:24,554 --> 01:07:27,368
Honestly, by God, you didn't push me?
Just tell the truth

844
01:07:27,488 --> 01:07:28,892
Didn't I say...
- Listen, Sir ...

845
01:07:29,012 --> 01:07:32,040
... let go of this "I kicked her out of
the house, but didn't push her" line

846
01:07:32,160 --> 01:07:35,067
... how far is it from the door to
the stairs? 2-3 meters?  - Yes

847
01:07:35,187 --> 01:07:37,947
So in this distance, what else could
happen?

848
01:07:38,067 --> 01:07:39,508
From our house to the hallway...

849
01:07:39,628 --> 01:07:41,160
Look, your Honor ...
- I am talking!

850
01:07:41,280 --> 01:07:44,640
You shouldn't be talking, only answering
- Be quiet!  - Did I interrupt you?

851
01:07:44,760 --> 01:07:48,600
You came here to give...  - Okay, fine
- I have questions you need to answer

852
01:07:48,720 --> 01:07:50,870
I have one question I want answered...

853
01:07:50,990 --> 01:07:53,435
... I want to ask him ...
- Ask, ask me

854
01:07:53,640 --> 01:07:57,330
If you've done nothing wrong,
what happened to her?

855
01:07:57,558 --> 01:08:00,753
... why did you come to the hospital?
- As a courtesy

856
01:08:00,873 --> 01:08:02,398
So you pushed her out of kindness?

857
01:08:02,520 --> 01:08:04,155
During the fight was anyone else
there?

858
01:08:04,275 --> 01:08:07,836
Yes, their neighbor were there.
- Okay, I'll subpoena her

859
01:08:07,960 --> 01:08:10,840
Your Honor, the neighbor will collude
just like the teacher

860
01:08:10,960 --> 01:08:12,757
From the beginning he has been...

861
01:08:12,877 --> 01:08:14,400
Am I lying?

862
01:08:14,520 --> 01:08:17,007
- I decide who is and isn't lying

863
01:08:17,127 --> 01:08:18,207
... be quiet.

864
01:08:18,327 --> 01:08:22,399
Sir, his wife, who wants a divorce,
brought him his bail money

865
01:08:22,520 --> 01:08:23,599
My God!

866
01:08:23,719 --> 01:08:25,920
Do you have a guarantor?
- What do you mean?

867
01:08:26,040 --> 01:08:28,880
They will need to be a civil servant
or business owner

868
01:08:29,000 --> 01:08:30,480
I have no one, my husband is unemployed
- Why does she need a guarantor?

869
01:08:30,600 --> 01:08:34,354
She's been charged...
- What is she charged with?

870
01:08:34,474 --> 01:08:36,670
According to his complaint ...

871
01:08:36,790 --> 01:08:38,200
He had no right to make a complaint!

872
01:08:38,320 --> 01:08:41,760
She admitted that she tied him up,
locked the door, and left

873
01:08:41,880 --> 01:08:44,110
I explained that..
- Sir, her baby is dead!

874
01:08:44,240 --> 01:08:45,593
Keep your voice down.

875
01:08:47,320 --> 01:08:50,596
Are you not ashamed?
You call yourself a man?

876
01:08:50,716 --> 01:08:52,159
- I said be quiet.

877
01:08:55,115 --> 01:08:58,230
For God's sake listen to us.

878
01:08:58,670 --> 01:09:05,880
He distorts everything, he hit my wife
and my son died... What more do you want?

879
01:09:06,000 --> 01:09:08,036
... listen to us poor ones also

880
01:09:08,156 --> 01:09:11,869
I told you if you didn't respect this
court I'd put you in jail for 3 days

881
01:09:12,262 --> 01:09:15,040
I lost everything I have.
Do you think I'm afraid of jail?

882
01:09:15,160 --> 01:09:16,752
... Be afraid of God...

883
01:09:17,727 --> 01:09:19,831
Mr. Azadi, call a deputy to arrest
him

884
01:09:19,960 --> 01:09:21,837
Sir, on the Koran, please don't call

885
01:09:23,314 --> 01:09:25,949
Let them take me.
- Okay, leave, don't make any noise

886
01:09:26,069 --> 01:09:29,026
Why should I make noise? I don't talk
and they take away my rights

887
01:09:29,146 --> 01:09:30,520
Get out!

888
01:09:30,640 --> 01:09:33,359
I'm going, Sir

889
01:09:33,619 --> 01:09:36,315
Please, let me take my helmet.

890
01:09:36,853 --> 01:09:38,600
Go out
- He'll go, he'll go himself

891
01:09:38,720 --> 01:09:41,234
For 10 years I worked my ass off at
a shoe repairer

892
01:09:41,400 --> 01:09:44,920
... they kicked me out like a dog, I said
the law will give you what you deserve..

893
01:09:45,040 --> 01:09:51,195
... I made a complaint that lasted a
year, after that they said you lost, go home

894
01:09:52,199 --> 01:09:54,399
This time I won't let that happen

895
01:09:54,519 --> 01:09:57,473
Not this time, this time it's different

896
01:09:57,593 --> 01:09:59,955
I have nothing to lose, my problem is...

897
01:10:00,075 --> 01:10:02,310
... I can't speak like this man

898
01:10:02,430 --> 01:10:04,232
I lose my temper and I can't speak

899
01:10:04,629 --> 01:10:05,958
- Don't! Go outside!

900
01:10:15,120 --> 01:10:19,272
Hodjat?
- I do not feel good.

901
01:10:20,320 --> 01:10:22,895
Go sit down... Let's go.

902
01:10:23,120 --> 01:10:25,554
What do you want with him?
- We need to take to him.

903
01:10:25,720 --> 01:10:27,153
I want to talk to him

904
01:10:27,280 --> 01:10:29,350
Don't go anywhere

905
01:10:36,160 --> 01:10:38,276
On the Koran, your Honor

906
01:10:38,400 --> 01:10:40,072
Let me talk.

907
01:10:40,192 --> 01:10:43,720
Your Honor, his nerves are shot, I swear
to God it's his nerves

908
01:10:43,840 --> 01:10:45,831
We've listened to him for days, but
he won't listen to us

909
01:10:45,951 --> 01:10:48,622
On the Koran, every over day this month
he has been in jail

910
01:10:48,742 --> 01:10:52,922
All his creditors have been after him,
and I've begged them to leave him alone

911
01:10:53,042 --> 01:10:56,790
Sir, look, I beg you, your Honor, please
look

912
01:10:57,862 --> 01:11:00,920
Look at this, please look

913
01:11:01,040 --> 01:11:04,418
Sir, can I ask as a favor that you let
him go this one time?

914
01:11:04,538 --> 01:11:08,628
Sir, I swear to God, I'm not lying

915
01:11:10,840 --> 01:11:14,435
Since he's lost his job he has developed
depression, he can't help it

916
01:11:14,640 --> 01:11:16,498
God is my witness

917
01:11:16,618 --> 01:11:19,950
Your Honor, please forgive him

918
01:11:22,160 --> 01:11:26,073
Go tell him to find you a guarantor,
quickly

919
01:11:26,200 --> 01:11:27,758
God bless.

920
01:11:27,878 --> 01:11:29,247
Do not leave the building.

921
01:11:29,367 --> 01:11:32,115
Okay, I will wait until he returns

922
01:11:35,240 --> 01:11:36,958
Will you ask her?

923
01:11:38,000 --> 01:11:41,197
She'll think I'm asking her back because
she brought me bail

924
01:11:41,317 --> 01:11:43,238
Let her think that

925
01:11:44,480 --> 01:11:47,074
Dad ... please, for God's sake...

926
01:11:49,360 --> 01:11:50,199
OK.

927
01:11:50,903 --> 01:11:52,513
Do you promise?

928
01:11:56,360 --> 01:11:58,237
Well, what is your promise going to be?

929
01:12:02,560 --> 01:12:03,959
Dad ...

930
01:12:04,957 --> 01:12:05,677
Yes?

931
01:12:08,257 --> 01:12:10,955
You didn't know Razieh was pregnant?

932
01:12:12,257 --> 01:12:12,892
No.

933
01:12:15,617 --> 01:12:18,713
Why?
- Nothing.

934
01:12:19,540 --> 01:12:21,153
So, why did you ask?

935
01:12:22,103 --> 01:12:24,443
Last night mom said you knew

936
01:12:24,731 --> 01:12:27,474
How would you mother know whether or
not I knew that?

937
01:12:27,800 --> 01:12:31,284
She said that night at the hospital
when you learned Razieh's baby died...

938
01:12:31,548 --> 01:12:33,408
... you didn't say anything

939
01:12:33,528 --> 01:12:37,759
You didn't ask, "she had a child?",
you weren't surprised

940
01:12:38,822 --> 01:12:42,189
In a case like that wouldn't you ask
if she was pregnant?

941
01:12:42,806 --> 01:12:44,872
... but you knew...

942
01:12:48,740 --> 01:12:51,193
Your mother just wants to say bad things
about me

943
01:13:06,831 --> 01:13:08,591
Will you tell her?

944
01:14:04,680 --> 01:14:06,875
Sweetie, I can't...

945
01:14:07,913 --> 01:14:09,878
Didn't you promise?

946
01:14:11,768 --> 01:14:13,673
I'm sorry.

947
01:14:23,037 --> 01:14:26,994
Which step was it?
- This one

948
01:14:27,114 --> 01:14:28,641
This one?
- This step

949
01:14:38,952 --> 01:14:41,720
Dad, go in for a minute, I'll be
right in

950
01:15:14,430 --> 01:15:17,188
Are you mad at me?
- No.

951
01:15:20,848 --> 01:15:22,912
Did you go upstairs?

952
01:15:23,164 --> 01:15:25,316
Yes, I went to see Mrs. Kalaniyi.

953
01:15:26,240 --> 01:15:27,615
What did you want with her?

954
01:15:27,735 --> 01:15:31,316
I told her they were coming to question
her tomorrow and to be careful

955
01:15:31,680 --> 01:15:33,591
What does she need to be careful of?

956
01:15:35,616 --> 01:15:40,476
Be careful, just to be careful, that
they would question her, that's all

957
01:15:40,920 --> 01:15:42,512
Is there a problem?

958
01:15:43,160 --> 01:15:46,357
As long as she tells the truth why does
she need to be careful?

959
01:15:54,314 --> 01:15:56,317
Termeh ...
- Yes?

960
01:15:56,440 --> 01:15:57,686
Come here

961
01:15:57,806 --> 01:16:00,389
I have my homework
- Leave it, come here one minute

962
01:16:01,438 --> 01:16:03,909
Okay, pretend I'm the woman

963
01:16:07,920 --> 01:16:11,680
Is that right? When someone gets pushed
they go straight

964
01:16:11,800 --> 01:16:19,434
They don't hit here, then here, then turn
around and hit here and fall there

965
01:16:19,554 --> 01:16:20,693
Right?

966
01:16:20,813 --> 01:16:23,426
If I had pushed her...

967
01:16:23,546 --> 01:16:26,961
... she would have either fallen on
these stairs...

968
01:16:27,081 --> 01:16:29,607
... or she would fall straight back and
hit here...

969
01:16:29,727 --> 01:16:31,730
I mean she couldn't fall here...

970
01:16:31,850 --> 01:16:34,236
Pretend you've been pushed, take the
path as if you had

971
01:16:34,356 --> 01:16:37,062
So, how did she fall then?
- I don't know.

972
01:16:37,182 --> 01:16:39,662
I'm just saying she didn't get thrown
onto these stairs

973
01:16:39,782 --> 01:16:41,912
Okay, now you come and stand here

974
01:16:42,032 --> 01:16:45,172
Why don't you tell them all this?
- Forget them

975
01:16:45,292 --> 01:16:47,869
I want you to know. Go on...

976
01:17:01,800 --> 01:17:05,434
Is this the direction he pushed you?
- No, he pushed me downwards

977
01:17:05,554 --> 01:17:10,186
Look, this door doesn't permit that...
it's not even possible

978
01:17:10,306 --> 01:17:11,582
You can't
- Where did you fall?

979
01:17:11,702 --> 01:17:14,634
On these stairs
- Which step?  - Excuse me

980
01:17:14,754 --> 01:17:16,111
I think this one

981
01:17:16,231 --> 01:17:18,158
You think, or you are sure?

982
01:17:18,527 --> 01:17:19,898
I'm not sure.

983
01:17:20,018 --> 01:17:22,033
Ma'am, is this where you found her?

984
01:17:22,153 --> 01:17:26,503
I didn't see her get pushed, but when I
arrived she was at the bottom stair

985
01:17:26,623 --> 01:17:29,918
Why aren't you saying anything? Go show
them how he pushed you

986
01:17:30,228 --> 01:17:32,503
I was ill, I swear to God, I didn't know
what was going on

987
01:17:32,623 --> 01:17:35,080
Look, I'll stand in the place of your
wife at the doorway

988
01:17:35,200 --> 01:17:38,040
... now, please stand here and with all
your strength...

989
01:17:38,160 --> 01:17:40,833
... push me, I'm saying it's not
even possible

990
01:17:40,953 --> 01:17:45,208
Of course you won't fall, but she's
a pregnant woman, if just one hand...

991
01:17:45,328 --> 01:17:48,950
Then you come, come here and elect
whoever you want to push you

992
01:17:49,070 --> 01:17:50,960
I'm saying it's not possible, excuse
me...

993
01:17:51,080 --> 01:17:53,480
I'm saying if you push from here she
won't fall that way

994
01:17:53,600 --> 01:17:56,478
What step? She says she fell on the
top step

995
