Everyone here says they found her on
that step

996
01:17:59,387 --> 01:18:01,486
Ma'am, did you see where she was pushed
from upstairs?

997
01:18:01,606 --> 01:18:06,152
Yes, I can't see the door from up here,
but I can see the stairwell where she fell

998
01:18:06,620 --> 01:18:08,500
Can you show me from where you saw it?

999
01:18:08,620 --> 01:18:10,772
Perhaps she was dizzy and fell.

1000
01:18:10,892 --> 01:18:14,672
How many times did you go up and down
these stairs? And she was never dizzy

1001
01:18:14,792 --> 01:18:18,629
Excuse me, that morning when I saw you
at the top of the stairs

1002
01:18:18,800 --> 01:18:22,110
I asked her why the garbage had spilled
on the stairs...

1003
01:18:22,230 --> 01:18:26,304
she said she had gotten dizzy and
dropped the bag, isn't that right?

1004
01:18:26,424 --> 01:18:30,515
My daughter took it out
- But, you said that you were dizzy

1005
01:18:30,640 --> 01:18:33,795
Ms. Kalani, weren't the stairs cleaned
that day?

1006
01:18:33,915 --> 01:18:36,600
Maybe the stairs were wet and she
slipped and fell

1007
01:18:36,720 --> 01:18:38,278
You asshole! You pushed her!

1008
01:18:38,398 --> 01:18:39,276
Be respectful!

1009
01:18:39,440 --> 01:18:41,066
I'm not talking back because your
family is here

1010
01:18:41,186 --> 01:18:43,600
Eat shit, asshole!
- Don't swear! Take him out

1011
01:18:43,720 --> 01:18:45,306
Go on
- Don't curse

1012
01:18:45,968 --> 01:18:49,317
They may need him tomorrow, they won't
say anything against him

1013
01:18:49,480 --> 01:18:52,240
If you're saying they are lying then
make a complaint

1014
01:18:52,360 --> 01:18:53,880
Are you telling the truth?

1015
01:18:54,000 --> 01:18:59,200
Fuck me, I spent the whole morning here,
and one says she fell here and the other
says she fell there

1016
01:18:59,320 --> 01:19:02,551
Excuse me, please give my daughter her
backpack

1017
01:19:12,375 --> 01:19:14,751
There you go.

1018
01:19:24,400 --> 01:19:26,755
Here you go, you don't want your
drawings?

1019
01:19:29,001 --> 01:19:33,074
Honey, don't let this fight with your
parents upset you

1020
01:19:33,321 --> 01:19:35,590
Come here, let me put it in your bag

1021
01:19:42,804 --> 01:19:47,193
My mother did not take your money.
- I know.

1022
01:19:48,520 --> 01:19:50,829
That's not the reason I was fighting
with her

1023
01:19:52,800 --> 01:19:55,567
Well then what for?

1024
01:19:55,687 --> 01:19:58,559
I was upset because she abandoned my
father and left

1025
01:20:01,325 --> 01:20:03,874
Well, she had gone to the doctor

1026
01:20:08,680 --> 01:20:10,159
Go ahead.

1027
01:20:12,049 --> 01:20:13,236
Be careful of the stairs

1028
01:20:13,356 --> 01:20:17,000
As per the order, we will examine him
and write down whatever we see

1029
01:20:17,120 --> 01:20:20,351
Doctor, well you see, he doesn't
speak

1030
01:20:20,799 --> 01:20:22,611
- Didn't you say he has Alzheimer's?

1031
01:20:22,731 --> 01:20:26,089
Yes, he has it, but before this he
spoke, he'd say things

1032
01:20:26,209 --> 01:20:28,914
- This is a doctor's office, not a court,
prove it there

1033
01:20:29,449 --> 01:20:33,719
- He got a bruise?
- Yes, a little one

1034
01:21:08,659 --> 01:21:10,199
- What happened?

1035
01:21:10,970 --> 01:21:14,277
I'm not sure if his bruising is a result
of falling out of the bed

1036
01:21:30,259 --> 01:21:31,878
Don't run, slow down

1037
01:21:32,575 --> 01:21:35,030
Put down the window, Mom, there
is a fight

1038
01:21:35,150 --> 01:21:37,048
- You see this is a girl's school

1039
01:21:38,371 --> 01:21:39,560
Hello

1040
01:21:39,680 --> 01:21:42,634
- You are not allowed to stand here

1041
01:21:42,754 --> 01:21:44,982
I have something to say

1042
01:21:45,102 --> 01:21:47,188
If you have a problem, talk to the
police

1043
01:21:47,308 --> 01:21:49,002
I just want to talk to this woman

1044
01:21:49,122 --> 01:21:52,640
I have nothing to say, I don't know
you or that woman's husband

1045
01:21:52,760 --> 01:21:55,406
- So, why did you lie in court?
- What lies?

1046
01:21:55,526 --> 01:21:58,400
- She knows the lie she told.
- Ms. Safaei, call the police.

1047
01:21:58,520 --> 01:22:02,433
<mumbles> - You have a problem with someone else,
what does this woman have to do with it?

1048
01:22:02,600 --> 01:22:05,188
If she has nothing to do with it why
was she talking to my daughter?

1049
01:22:05,308 --> 01:22:06,833
What do I have to do with your
daughter?

1050
01:22:07,000 --> 01:22:10,117
You are a teacher of this country,
are you not ashamed?

1051
01:22:10,280 --> 01:22:13,238
Why did you tell her that her dad hit
her mom and she had a miscarriage?

1052
01:22:13,358 --> 01:22:14,320
