1053
01:22:14,440 --> 01:22:18,094
Aren't you ashamed of looking at the
picture by a 4 year old and telling ...

1054
01:22:18,214 --> 01:22:20,031
... her that her dad hit her mom and
caused the miscarriage?

1055
01:22:20,151 --> 01:22:21,235
That's not what I said

1056
01:22:21,360 --> 01:22:24,636
Why are you saying that I hit my wife
and kids like some kind of animal?

1057
01:22:25,138 --> 01:22:27,676
I swear on this Koran that I am a human
just like you

1058
01:22:32,771 --> 01:22:34,196
- Get up, please

1059
01:22:35,635 --> 01:22:37,870
Ma'am, I have nothing in my life to lose

1060
01:22:38,000 --> 01:22:41,551
Tell your husband not to do anything
that will make me lose my mind

1061
01:22:41,671 --> 01:22:43,650
Ma'am, I will
- Go on, sir

1062
01:22:44,466 --> 01:22:46,914
Come on, just go

1063
01:22:47,034 --> 01:22:50,869
I'm unemployed, I will stand at the door
to this school day and night

1064
01:22:51,040 --> 01:22:55,600
Either go to court and tell them you
lied or I will dig deep to uncover your
relationship with her husband

1065
01:22:55,720 --> 01:22:58,880
Shame on you, sir, I've kept my mouth
shut and you...

1066
01:22:59,000 --> 01:23:02,880
- So, why are you protecting him?
- The court asked questions and I told
the truth.

1067
01:23:03,000 --> 01:23:04,353
- You told the truth?
- Yes!

1068
01:23:04,480 --> 01:23:07,120
Put your hand on this Koran and
swear to it.

1069
01:23:07,240 --> 01:23:09,480
Why do you need an oath? Who do you
think you are?

1070
01:23:09,600 --> 01:23:11,511
I'm not afraid, what do you
want me to say?

1071
01:23:11,640 --> 01:23:14,920
You told the court her husband didn't
know my wife was pregnant

1072
01:23:15,040 --> 01:23:16,189
- Yes.
- Swear to that

1073
01:23:16,320 --> 01:23:18,675
I swear on the Koran that on the day I
was at their house...

1074
01:23:18,840 --> 01:23:23,516
... her husband did not hear our
conversation because he was in the kitchen

1075
01:23:24,082 --> 01:23:26,754
Is this good, or do you want me to say
something else?

1076
01:23:31,320 --> 01:23:32,548
He's insane

1077
01:23:35,788 --> 01:23:38,553
- Where are you going? Call your
husband, don't go alone

1078
01:23:38,673 --> 01:23:40,660
No, I don't want him to know.

1079
01:23:40,780 --> 01:23:43,310
Why are you standing there?

1080
01:23:44,493 --> 01:23:45,755
Hello?

1081
01:23:47,469 --> 01:23:52,568
Hello, Mrs. Qahraei.
I left you a message.

1082
01:23:53,280 --> 01:23:55,541
Could you please pick up the phone?

1083
01:23:59,440 --> 01:24:03,558
The woman who was coming to our house
for my father...

1084
01:24:03,678 --> 01:24:07,094
... she got the number of a gynecologist
from you?

1085
01:24:07,510 --> 01:24:10,376
I wanted to ask you to please give
me that number

1086
01:24:10,853 --> 01:24:14,239
... so I can call him to see if she went
to his office that week ...

1087
01:24:14,359 --> 01:24:19,350
... and if she did what the problem was.
I would appreciate it if you could call
me back.

1088
01:24:34,800 --> 01:24:36,358
What do you want to do?

1089
01:24:37,840 --> 01:24:39,671
What?

1090
01:24:40,640 --> 01:24:42,995
You want this fight to continue every
day?

1091
01:24:43,200 --> 01:24:44,474
Why? What happened?

1092
01:24:44,594 --> 01:24:48,235
Today he went to school and embarrassed
our child in front of everyone

1093
01:24:50,886 --> 01:24:52,388
What did he say?

1094
01:24:52,699 --> 01:24:56,999
He yelled in front of everyone that my
father killed his child

1095
01:24:59,155 --> 01:25:01,111
- How can she go to school any more?

1096
01:25:02,116 --> 01:25:03,992
Do you realize what you are doing?

1097
01:25:04,900 --> 01:25:07,031
What I am doing?

1098
01:25:10,077 --> 01:25:12,834
He is causing problems.
- He has no right.

1099
01:25:14,682 --> 01:25:16,517
Termeh, go to your room.

1100
01:25:22,479 --> 01:25:25,069
If tomorrow he goes to school and kills
you daughter, then what?

1101
01:25:26,139 --> 01:25:29,057
What do you want me to do?
Pack up and move abroad?

1102
01:25:29,177 --> 01:25:32,636
Forget abroad, I'm here trying to talk
to you about...

1103
01:25:32,800 --> 01:25:36,429
... Termeh and this situation you have
created for her.

1104
01:25:36,689 --> 01:25:40,919
I created this situation? You have some
nerve to say that to me.

1105
01:25:41,354 --> 01:25:44,412
Who left their spouse and child?
Who asked for a divorce?

1106
01:25:44,532 --> 01:25:47,558
You are the one that said to go
- Yeah, then why are you back?

1107
01:25:47,678 --> 01:25:49,877
I'm not back, I'm here to sort out
my daughter's situation.

1108
01:25:49,997 --> 01:25:50,992
It's sorted

1109
01:25:51,112 --> 01:25:54,200
You have two options ...
- Do not threaten me.

1110
01:25:54,320 --> 01:25:55,799
What threat?

1111
01:25:56,392 --> 01:25:58,520
You need to solve your problem with this
guy...

1112
01:25:58,640 --> 01:26:00,920
No, I know how to deal with him
- Didn't you hit her?

1113
01:26:01,040 --> 01:26:03,176
Didn't you throw her down the stairs?
Didn't her child die?

1114
01:26:03,296 --> 01:26:05,320
Yes! I killed her child!

1115
01:26:05,440 --> 01:26:08,216
Why are you being so stubborn? Put an
end to all of this

1116
01:26:08,336 --> 01:26:10,560
I am not paying money by force.
- How is it forced?

1117
01:26:10,680 --> 01:26:11,774
Put yourself in their place.

1118
01:26:11,894 --> 01:26:14,919
I'm not responsible for their troubles
- Their child is dead

1119
01:26:15,039 --> 01:26:19,756
Yeah, and my dad is handicapped, come
and see. He doesn't speak a word to me

1120
01:26:20,080 --> 01:26:21,798
It's not like he talked a lot before
this

1121
01:26:22,040 --> 01:26:24,880
He spoke few words, but those few words
made me happy

1122
01:26:25,000 --> 01:26:26,680
This doesn't compare to her situation

1123
01:26:26,800 --> 01:26:28,836
And how do you know that I hit her?

1124
01:26:30,287 --> 01:26:32,378
So how did the child die?
- I don't know

1125
01:26:32,942 --> 01:26:36,158
I don't know. For one moment consider...

1126
01:26:36,280 --> 01:26:39,795
... that when she left, her husband did
something to her and she blamed me.

1127
01:26:39,915 --> 01:26:42,680
Her daughter said they went to the
doctor that day

1128
01:26:42,800 --> 01:26:45,983
What was so wrong that she couldn't
wait 2 hours and go in the afternoon?

1129
01:26:46,103 --> 01:26:48,640
Why did she tie this old man to the bed
and leave?

1130
01:26:48,760 --> 01:26:51,228
The doctor said the child's death was
the result of a blow

1131
01:26:51,400 --> 01:26:54,153
A blow? Why does it have to be a blow
from me?

1132
01:26:54,384 --> 01:26:56,995
Not until it is proven to be, will I
let it go

1133
01:26:59,760 --> 01:27:02,096
Okay, I'll take Termeh

1134
01:27:02,216 --> 01:27:05,676
Shame on you. All this is going on
and you're using it to pressure me

1135
01:27:05,840 --> 01:27:07,119
I'm worried for Termeh

1136
01:27:07,239 --> 01:27:09,807
Termeh wants to live here and she needs
to learn at school

1137
01:27:09,927 --> 01:27:12,110
Learn what? How to fight and
antagonize?

1138
01:27:12,230 --> 01:27:14,710
No, learn how not to be a coward
like you.

1139
01:27:14,830 --> 01:27:17,292
So that any time someone yells at her
she'll back down

1140
01:27:17,412 --> 01:27:20,101
And he knows who to antagonize and not
to antagonize

1141
01:27:20,353 --> 01:27:22,040
Yes, I am coward.

1142
01:27:22,160 --> 01:27:28,115
You know what your problem is? Any time
you're faced with any difficulty...

1143
01:27:28,235 --> 01:27:34,276
... rather than deal with it, you run
away or raise your hands and surrender

1144
01:27:34,440 --> 01:27:36,299
Give me one reason you want to leave
this country.

1145
01:27:36,419 --> 01:27:37,614
You're afraid to stay.

1146
01:27:37,734 --> 01:27:40,926
Sorry, I wasn't here for a week and you
couldn't run the household

1147
01:27:41,046 --> 01:27:43,509
I couldn't, and I'm responsible.

1148
01:27:44,040 --> 01:27:47,112
Let me take Termeh, and you do whatever
you want to do

1149
01:27:50,172 --> 01:27:52,396
Termeh, honey, don't make any decision
on my account

1150
01:27:52,620 --> 01:27:54,751
Go wherever you are comfortable.

1151
01:27:59,488 --> 01:28:01,352
You still don't want to come?

1152
01:28:12,204 --> 01:28:13,836
It's sold for $20,000 rial

1153
01:28:13,956 --> 01:28:18,188
If every you use 270kg of flour...

1154
01:28:19,371 --> 01:28:24,310
... what is the profit each day?

1155
01:28:24,948 --> 01:28:26,599
How would you solve this?

1156
01:28:27,119 --> 01:28:28,958
Did you lie?

1157
01:28:30,480 --> 01:28:31,708
What?

1158
01:28:33,040 --> 01:28:34,632
Are you lying?

1159
01:28:35,600 --> 01:28:37,079
About what?

1160
01:28:38,523 --> 01:28:41,718
That you didn't know the woman was
pregnant?

1161
01:28:43,101 --> 01:28:44,514
Why?

1162
01:28:45,782 --> 01:28:50,397
You said when Ms. Qahraei and Razieh
were talking you didn't hear anything

1163
01:28:50,878 --> 01:28:52,114
Yes.

1164
01:28:52,234 --> 01:28:56,758
So when did you hear Ms. Qahraei gave
Razieh the gynecologist's number?

1165
01:28:57,759 --> 01:29:00,111
Wasn't she told it during the same
conversation?

1166
01:29:09,011 --> 01:29:09,755
Okay

1167
01:29:10,931 --> 01:29:13,913
So, if you want to calculate...

1168
01:29:19,410 --> 01:29:21,676
Yes, I knew.

1169
01:29:22,986 --> 01:29:24,951
Your mother is telling the truth.

1170
01:29:27,070 --> 01:29:31,917
When she was talking to you teacher in
the hall I heard it all from the kitchen

1171
01:29:33,400 --> 01:29:35,391
So why did you say you did not know?

1172
01:29:38,680 --> 01:29:42,093
Do you know what would have happened if
I said that I knew?

1173
01:29:44,640 --> 01:29:47,438
1 to 3 years in prison.

1174
01:29:48,084 --> 01:29:51,477
And I thought of what would happen
to you...

1175
01:29:52,524 --> 01:29:53,949
... who would you stay with?

1176
01:29:55,120 --> 01:29:56,951
I said I did not know.

1177
01:29:59,600 --> 01:30:01,556
If you knew, why did you push her?

1178
01:30:01,676 --> 01:30:05,190
I knew she was pregnant but at that
moment I didn't know

1179
01:30:05,457 --> 01:30:08,632
I had forgotten. I wasn't paying
attention.

1180
01:30:14,153 --> 01:30:15,896
So, tell them that.

1181
01:30:19,733 --> 01:30:21,520
The law doesn't get it

1182
01:30:22,582 --> 01:30:24,757
They'll say either you knew or you
didn't

1183
01:30:31,920 --> 01:30:33,399
Look at me.

1184
01:30:34,093 --> 01:30:36,635
If you want me to, I'll tell them

1185
01:31:27,767 --> 01:31:29,638
Hello.
- Hello.

1186
01:31:34,238 --> 01:31:37,343
Didn't I say not to come to the front
of the school?

1187
01:31:56,753 --> 01:31:58,194
Ms. Qahraei!

1188
01:32:08,983 --> 01:32:10,519
What do you want with her?

1189
01:32:10,843 --> 01:32:13,548
Ms. Qahraei, wait ...

1190
01:32:13,668 --> 01:32:17,430
If you can wait one second, I want to
explain something, that's all.

1191
01:32:18,013 --> 01:32:20,398
Please allow me... see... why...

1192
01:32:20,857 --> 01:32:22,474
Father!

1193
01:32:25,278 --> 01:32:27,303
Who is responsible for the safety of my
child?

1194
01:32:27,423 --> 01:32:29,160
I can't take action if there is no
witness

1195
01:32:29,280 --> 01:32:32,955
If I have no witness I just wait until
he kills my child?

1196
01:32:33,080 --> 01:32:36,834
- How do I know you're telling the truth?
- What reason do I have to lie?

1197
01:32:36,960 --> 01:32:41,480
Your Honor, I bring my wife and daughter
here to lie to you?

1198
01:32:41,600 --> 01:32:45,432
Your daughter is here now?
- Yes, outside, call her in, ask her.

1199
01:32:45,680 --> 01:32:49,389
I am afraid to take her to school.
I'm afraid to leave my father at home.

1200
01:32:50,680 --> 01:32:54,155
Is the plaintiff here?  - I can't leave
my dad at home.  - Are you done writing?

1201
01:32:54,880 --> 01:32:55,915
Almost done

1202
01:32:56,560 --> 01:32:58,477
You didn't know his wife was pregnant?

1203
01:32:58,597 --> 01:32:59,835
No, I didn't know.

1204
01:32:59,955 --> 01:33:03,310
When she was talking to the teacher
about the pregnancy you didn't overhear?

1205
01:33:03,430 --> 01:33:04,706
No, I did not hear

1206
01:33:05,880 --> 01:33:07,200
You didn't hear, huh?

1207
01:33:07,320 --> 01:33:09,737
I'm saying I didn't hear them...

1208
01:33:09,966 --> 01:33:12,642
The teacher came and withdrew her
statement.

1209
01:33:12,920 --> 01:33:14,148
- She says you knew

1210
01:33:14,520 --> 01:33:17,141
- She came and said that I knew?
- Yes, she came in yesterday

1211
01:33:17,261 --> 01:33:19,112
He went to the school and threatened her

1212
01:33:19,280 --> 01:33:21,840
No, answer my question, did you hear
them talking?

1213
01:33:21,960 --> 01:33:24,729
No I didn't.  - How did you know she
gave her the doctor's number?

1214
01:33:24,849 --> 01:33:27,076
My daughter told me
- What did she say?

1215
01:33:27,196 --> 01:33:30,637
That she got the number from the teacher

1216
01:33:30,840 --> 01:33:32,637
Tell your daughter to come in

1217
01:33:33,920 --> 01:33:35,273
Now?

1218
01:33:36,280 --> 01:33:37,599
You wait outside

1219
01:33:38,720 --> 01:33:39,914
What question?

1220
01:33:44,360 --> 01:33:45,918
What does he want to ask?

1221
01:33:48,920 --> 01:33:50,797
I do not know. Here, give it to me.

1222
01:33:58,040 --> 01:33:59,632
- What is your statement?

1223
01:34:00,120 --> 01:34:01,792
You haven't asked anything.

1224
01:34:02,360 --> 01:34:04,749
Did your father tell you what I would
ask while outside?

1225
01:34:05,400 --> 01:34:07,520
No.
- Which grade are you?

1226
01:34:07,640 --> 01:34:08,834
Sixth

1227
01:34:09,520 --> 01:34:13,559
On the day your teacher was at your
house and was talking to the care giver...

1228
01:34:13,720 --> 01:34:17,235
... about being pregnant, were you there?

1229
01:34:17,749 --> 01:34:21,276
At that time? No, I had gone to get my
books.

1230
01:34:21,652 --> 01:34:25,395
So, how did you know your teacher gave
the number to that woman?

1231
01:34:27,212 --> 01:34:30,680
She gave her the number after, when the
care giver was leaving

1232
01:34:30,800 --> 01:34:33,439
In front of you?
- Yes.

1233
01:34:33,600 --> 01:34:35,280
Why didn't you tell your father earlier?

1234
01:34:35,400 --> 01:34:36,212
What?

1235
01:34:36,332 --> 01:34:39,637
That the woman got the doctor's number
from your teacher

1236
01:34:40,280 --> 01:34:43,590
I didn't think it would be important to
my dad.

1237
01:34:45,160 --> 01:34:48,152
So did you tell your dad, or did he hear
it himself?

1238
01:34:48,600 --> 01:34:52,513
About the doctor's number? I told him.

1239
01:34:53,097 --> 01:34:55,071
You told him?
- Yes.

1240
01:34:56,440 --> 01:34:57,839
Okay, go

1241
01:35:46,640 --> 01:35:49,996
What crime have I committed?
- Nothing. You're right.

1242
01:35:50,640 --> 01:35:52,440
Your husband does not accept
responsibility.

1243
01:35:52,560 --> 01:35:55,812
I accept he is responsible, but to what
end?

1244
01:35:55,932 --> 01:35:58,120
To spend one year, two years in court...

1245
01:35:58,240 --> 01:36:00,200
... so that you get 100,000 toman a
month?

1246
01:36:00,320 --> 01:36:04,300
This is what saddens me, why do you
think I'm going to court for money?

1247
01:36:04,568 --> 01:36:05,815
When did I say that?

1248
01:36:05,935 --> 01:36:08,276
You think I'm a bum and my child has
died...

1249
01:36:08,440 --> 01:36:12,027
... and we don't understand anything.
- No, I didn't say that

1250
01:36:12,147 --> 01:36:14,133
- Wait, let's see what she has to say

1251
01:36:14,253 --> 01:36:18,115
This is not the way to go... All of this
won't bring back your child...

1252
01:36:18,235 --> 01:36:20,039
... and my husband won't be killed

1253
01:36:20,320 --> 01:36:23,240
Her husband didn't' do it intentionally.

1254
01:36:23,360 --> 01:36:26,193
- They are good people, they are trying
to find a solution

1255
01:36:26,560 --> 01:36:29,711
Take the money and put it to good use

1256
01:36:30,280 --> 01:36:33,750
Let's come to an agreement right now.
Leave convincing my husband to me.

1257
01:36:35,560 --> 01:36:40,031
He needs convincing? Leave us alone...

1258
01:36:41,840 --> 01:36:44,240
They're trying to make peace...

1259
01:36:44,360 --> 01:36:47,318
... take a look at yourself.
- Sir, please don't let him go

1260
01:36:50,760 --> 01:36:53,194
Wait a minute, I want to talk to you.

1261
01:37:24,590 --> 01:37:27,110
Hello.
- Hello.

1262
01:37:41,652 --> 01:37:43,153
Will you stay?

1263
01:37:45,600 --> 01:37:46,531
Mom...

1264
01:37:49,360 --> 01:37:51,237
Let us have our talk

1265
01:38:00,160 --> 01:38:02,390
Come, sit down, I want to talk to you.

1266
01:38:04,920 --> 01:38:06,319
I'm listening

1267
01:38:08,200 --> 01:38:11,237
Today I went to talk with her husband.

1268
01:38:12,000 --> 01:38:13,274
Sit down.

1269
01:38:24,000 --> 01:38:30,221
I talked to him and after negotiating, I
got him to agree to $15 million rather
than $40 million

1270
01:38:30,341 --> 01:38:32,851
Three checks of $5 million

1271
01:38:33,800 --> 01:38:35,995
How dare you promise him the money?

1272
01:38:36,320 --> 01:38:39,508
I can't constantly stress about my child's
safety.  - You don't understand what I'm
saying

1273
01:38:39,628 --> 01:38:42,152
Even now because you were late I was
dying of worry

1274
01:38:42,272 --> 01:38:45,040
I'm saying why are you butting in?

1275
01:38:46,050 --> 01:38:47,836
I didn't come here to fight

1276
01:38:48,040 --> 01:38:50,000
God, why can't she understand?

1277
01:38:50,120 --> 01:38:53,432
Aren't you saying I'm at fault? Aren't
you saying that I introduced you to her?

1278
01:38:53,560 --> 01:38:56,711
Aren't you saying none of this would
happen if I had not left?

1279
01:38:56,880 --> 01:38:58,160
So let me fix it

1280
01:38:58,280 --> 01:39:01,920
But if I tell him I'll pay, I'm
admitting responsibility

1281
01:39:02,040 --> 01:39:04,518
He agreed to it.
- He's not going to leave us alone.

1282
01:39:04,638 --> 01:39:07,560
You think he'll leave us alone if you
don't pay? - Why should I pay him?

1283
01:39:07,680 --> 01:39:08,999
Pretend it's my dowry.

1284
01:39:09,448 --> 01:39:14,720
If I need to beg for it, or borrow it,
you'll get your dowry back

1285
01:39:14,840 --> 01:39:17,631
But as for the money for him, I neither
have it, nor will I give it

1286
01:39:17,751 --> 01:39:20,997
Our child is in puberty, she's already
suffering because of that

1287
01:39:21,440 --> 01:39:26,673
So you understand the sensitivity of our
daughter during puberty?

1288
01:39:27,814 --> 01:39:29,599
If she was suffering she wouldn't stay

1289
01:39:29,967 --> 01:39:32,236
Why do you think she is staying
with you?

1290
01:39:32,585 --> 01:39:34,552
She chose you?

1291
01:39:35,840 --> 01:39:37,990
She stayed with you so we don't divorce

1292
01:39:39,907 --> 01:39:42,195
She knows I won't go anywhere without
her.

1293
01:39:44,040 --> 01:39:46,759
She is suffering, but she is hiding it.

1294
01:39:51,022 --> 01:39:55,863
You'll call him now and tell him your
husband won't pay until fault is proven.

1295
01:39:56,443 --> 01:39:58,119
I'll sell my car.

1296
01:39:58,884 --> 01:40:02,277
I don't want you to sell your car for me
- It's not for you

1297
01:40:02,600 --> 01:40:04,760
If your child is not valuable enough...

1298
01:40:04,880 --> 01:40:07,633
What bullshit are you talking? This
isn't about money.

1299
01:40:07,760 --> 01:40:11,036
Until the safety of my child is secured,
I can't let this go.

1300
01:40:11,156 --> 01:40:13,469
You no longer have a right to do
anything

1301
01:40:13,717 --> 01:40:15,069
Do you understand?

1302
01:40:15,480 --> 01:40:18,233
If I had done nothing, you'd be in jail
right now.

1303
01:40:22,040 --> 01:40:24,971
Make an appointment with the court and
request the bail money back.

1304
01:40:25,091 --> 01:40:28,455
I don't want to be out of prison because
of your bail money

1305
01:40:45,240 --> 01:40:48,198
Get up, Termeh.
Get up, let's go.

1306
01:40:48,320 --> 01:40:49,912
Get up, I tell you.

1307
01:40:50,200 --> 01:40:51,792
Mother, please.

1308
01:40:53,800 --> 01:40:57,793
I don't want to stay here any more.
- No, Mom, I won't let you.

1309
01:40:57,960 --> 01:41:00,679
$15 million is worth more to you, you
put your child in the middle of this

1310
01:41:00,840 --> 01:41:02,478
I will not let you do it.

1311
01:41:02,760 --> 01:41:05,149
When you don't value your child
enough to...

1312
01:41:05,280 --> 01:41:07,316
Mom, what are you doing?
- When you see your child's life...

1313
01:41:07,480 --> 01:41:08,754
You said you would stay.

1314
01:41:08,874 --> 01:41:11,519
I was stupid to say that.
- Mom, please!

1315
01:41:11,639 --> 01:41:14,534
- For the love of God, please
- I'm waiting for you in the car.

1316
01:41:25,440 --> 01:41:28,955
It's okay, go for a few days until the
end of exams.

1317
01:41:29,639 --> 01:41:31,836
Your grandma and grandpa are there too

1318
01:41:32,112 --> 01:41:35,676
You'll be more comfortable
- Didn't you say it wasn't serious?

1319
01:41:36,641 --> 01:41:38,233
It became serious

1320
01:41:39,680 --> 01:41:41,113
Termeh ...

1321
01:41:41,691 --> 01:41:43,392
Honey ...

1322
01:41:44,730 --> 01:41:46,720
If you cry, honey, I'll cry.

1323
01:41:46,840 --> 01:41:49,527
Why won't you pay him the money so that
Mom will come back?

1324
01:41:49,647 --> 01:41:51,948
Mom coming back has nothing to do with
this money, honey.

1325
01:41:52,068 --> 01:41:56,685
Yes, she was going to stay, I saw the
luggage in the car.

1326
01:42:35,583 --> 01:42:38,628
If you think I'm guilty, go get your
mom and tell her to come in

1327
01:42:38,865 --> 01:42:41,553
We'll call them and arrange to go and
give them the money

1328
01:43:55,165 --> 01:43:56,457
I have doubts.

1329
01:43:56,724 --> 01:43:58,678
Didn't he throw you?

1330
01:43:58,972 --> 01:43:59,715
Yes.

1331
01:44:00,967 --> 01:44:03,469
When you went home, did something
happen?

1332
01:44:04,398 --> 01:44:06,875
No, even before my child was not moving.

1333
01:44:07,828 --> 01:44:09,633
Before he threw you?

1334
01:44:15,040 --> 01:44:17,429
You mean the child died before?

1335
01:44:18,000 --> 01:44:22,073
I do not know. Maybe.
- Had something happened before?

1336
01:44:24,160 --> 01:44:27,887
I'm not sure, but I had pain the
previous night.

1337
01:44:29,363 --> 01:44:31,875
Have you ever had a miscarriage before?
- No.

1338
01:44:34,840 --> 01:44:36,637
I was hit by a car.

1339
01:44:43,152 --> 01:44:47,717
Your father-in-law went into the street.
I put on my chador and went after him.

1340
01:44:49,280 --> 01:44:52,720
He was trying to cross the street and I
ran to get him...

1341
01:44:52,840 --> 01:44:55,832
... so a car wouldn't hit him, but a
car hit me.

1342
01:44:56,438 --> 01:44:58,193
That night the pain began.

1343
01:45:01,160 --> 01:45:03,116
Does your husband know about this?

1344
01:45:04,864 --> 01:45:07,549
Why didn't you say this in court?

1345
01:45:09,200 --> 01:45:12,954
My husband would kill himself if he
found out I came here and told you this.

1346
01:45:14,457 --> 01:45:19,588
He's been crying since he pledged the
money to his creditors yesterday

1347
01:45:20,105 --> 01:45:23,670
What fault does my husband have? Do you
know how much this damaged our lives?

1348
01:45:26,654 --> 01:45:28,393
That's my fault.

1349
01:45:32,000 --> 01:45:34,722
Yesterday when he told me that you
promised him the money...

1350
01:45:34,842 --> 01:45:38,232
... I got very scared and I called a few
places and asked...

1351
01:45:38,895 --> 01:45:42,437
They said if you have any doubts it is a
sin to accept the money.

1352
01:45:43,038 --> 01:45:46,082
If we don't pay this money then we will
have to prove my husband is innocent.

1353
01:45:46,202 --> 01:45:49,477
You promised not to repeat what I just
told you

1354
01:45:49,597 --> 01:45:52,120
But your husband will not leave us
alone...

1355
01:45:52,240 --> 01:45:53,542
I fear for my child.

1356
01:45:53,662 --> 01:45:57,754
I'm afraid if sinful money comes into my
house that something will happen to her

1357
01:45:58,175 --> 01:46:00,118
What do you want from me?

1358
01:46:01,480 --> 01:46:03,072
Don't pay the money.

1359
01:46:04,309 --> 01:46:05,749
Don't pay.

1360
01:46:12,840 --> 01:46:14,751
Will your husband leave us alone,
though?

1361
01:46:46,731 --> 01:46:49,553
Give that to me, bring some small
plates.

1362
01:46:50,840 --> 01:46:52,796
Don't worry, nothing will happen.

1363
01:47:12,797 --> 01:47:18,633
When you withdraw your complaint from
the court we will give you the 3 checks.

1364
01:47:18,990 --> 01:47:20,326
God bless.

1365
01:47:20,594 --> 01:47:24,793
Get a pen and paper, let's write all of
this down and sign it

1366
01:47:25,613 --> 01:47:27,630
I have one thing to say before...

1367
01:47:27,750 --> 01:47:29,563
Let's just finish this

1368
01:47:29,683 --> 01:47:37,850
I just want his wife and my daughter to
come in, I have something to say...

1369
01:47:40,448 --> 01:47:42,153
Why won't she come?

1370
01:47:43,960 --> 01:47:45,234
Thank you.

1371
01:47:46,215 --> 01:47:48,510
Please, call my daughter also.

1372
01:47:51,906 --> 01:47:53,957
Termeh, your father is calling for you.

1373
01:47:59,108 --> 01:47:59,880
Hello

1374
01:48:05,242 --> 01:48:08,026
Termeh, come and sit here.

1375
01:48:14,276 --> 01:48:15,756
Excuse me

1376
01:48:17,820 --> 01:48:18,705
Look ...

1377
01:48:19,054 --> 01:48:22,636
I wrote checks and will give them to
you, no issues.

1378
01:48:22,954 --> 01:48:24,269
It's done

1379
01:48:24,730 --> 01:48:26,592
I have one favor to ask, if I may.

1380
01:48:27,202 --> 01:48:29,476
Ma'am, you're a religious woman

1381
01:48:30,698 --> 01:48:34,396
Bring a Koran and swear that I caused
your miscarriage.

1382
01:48:42,400 --> 01:48:44,311
Bring a Koran

1383
01:48:44,765 --> 01:48:46,274
Can you go grab it?

1384
01:49:02,754 --> 01:49:05,155
Come back soon, or they will start to
doubt...

1385
01:49:06,760 --> 01:49:11,151
Creditors are here for the money.
Don't ruin his reputation.

1386
01:49:13,175 --> 01:49:14,631
I will not swear

1387
01:49:16,360 --> 01:49:19,557
Didn't you say you went after his father
and were hit by a car?

1388
01:49:21,596 --> 01:49:25,632
Why won't you come?
- I'm afraid to swear to it.

1389
01:49:27,035 --> 01:49:31,092
Why?
- I have doubts

1390
01:49:37,520 --> 01:49:39,317
God ...

1391
01:49:40,276 --> 01:49:42,512
Azam, go and sit down with them.

1392
01:49:45,303 --> 01:49:48,892
Why are you telling me this now?

1393
01:49:50,090 --> 01:49:51,991
I swear I told Azam

1394
01:49:53,470 --> 01:49:55,549
Tell me exactly what happened

1395
01:49:58,969 --> 01:50:02,072
The day before the miscarriage I was
hit by a car...

1396
01:50:02,360 --> 01:50:04,874
... and that night I had a lot of pain.

1397
01:50:14,480 --> 01:50:17,080
- Let's go, it's already settled.
- No.

1398
01:50:17,200 --> 01:50:18,840
It is a sin. I asked.

1399
01:50:18,960 --> 01:50:22,000
He's agreed to pay it, let's go.

1400
01:50:22,120 --> 01:50:24,880
I'm scared, God will curse us.

1401
01:50:25,000 --> 01:50:28,276
What have you done? Look at me...

1402
01:50:28,400 --> 01:50:32,120
... think of my situation, show some
mercy

1403
01:50:32,240 --> 01:50:35,688
I'm afraid something will happen to our
child if we go through with this.

1404
01:50:36,118 --> 01:50:37,711
- Let's go.
- I can't.

1405
01:50:37,939 --> 01:50:40,535
- Let's go.
- I can't.

1406
01:50:40,891 --> 01:50:44,875
I can't, oh God, I can't

1407
01:50:46,698 --> 01:50:49,861
Don't hit me, don't hit me

1408
01:51:08,695 --> 01:51:12,811
Ma'am, why did you come here tonight?
Didn't I tell you not to?

1409
01:51:13,039 --> 01:51:15,310
Didn't I say the money is sinful and we
didn't want it?

1410
01:51:15,537 --> 01:51:17,995
How am I supposed to live here now?

1411
01:51:18,979 --> 01:51:21,510
Why have you done this to me?

1412
01:52:45,169 --> 01:52:46,635
Come on.

1413
01:52:51,440 --> 01:52:53,158
Come on, let's go.

1414
01:53:06,938 --> 01:53:09,760
Hello.
- Hello. Come in..

1415
01:53:19,123 --> 01:53:21,351
Yes, so what is the decision?

1416
01:53:21,583 --> 01:53:26,592
Okay, your mom and dad have left it up
to you to decide where to live after
the divorce

1417
01:53:26,712 --> 01:53:29,837
Do you want to be with your dad or your
mom?

1418
01:53:30,585 --> 01:53:32,836
- Have you made your decision?
- Yes.

1419
01:53:33,716 --> 01:53:35,272
- Are you sure?
- Yes.

1420
01:53:45,680 --> 01:53:48,399
- Have you made up your mind, or not?
- Yes.

1421
01:53:50,879 --> 01:53:52,598
- So what is it, my dear?

1422
01:53:54,099 --> 01:53:56,191
Do I have to say it now?

1423
01:53:57,121 --> 01:53:59,675
- If you still haven't...
- No, I have thought about it...

1424
01:54:04,231 --> 01:54:06,471
- If you haven't decided
- No, I have

1425
01:54:06,719 --> 01:54:07,398
And?

1426
01:54:09,020 --> 01:54:12,010
Do you want them to wait outside if
it's too hard?

1427
01:54:12,952 --> 01:54:14,713
Is that okay?

1428
01:54:15,277 --> 01:54:17,118
Sir, wait outside for a minute.

1429
01:54:19,503 --> 01:54:21,669
You too, ma'am.

